{
  "stem": "24231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, there were Czech, mostly Czech fellows there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then later on, people from Germany came there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of the Jews, surprisingly, you know, they thought they going to a-- to a recreation place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they brought in all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they confiscated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans confiscated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And later on, they came out with ghetto money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you were able to buy with that-- depending what kind of a job you had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they were paid so much, so much of this money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you were able to buy somebody else's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They made up phony stores, you know, stores for show, for the visits of these Swiss-- Swiss teams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you would be buying somebody else's stuff, all the stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at least you were buying something which you needed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and some of the German people, very old, very old, most of them were older people, they would be bringing in [SIGHS] all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Naturally, jewelry they would confiscate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But clothing and stuff like that they would be putting into these stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then later on, some of-- some Hungarian Jews came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some Dutch Jews came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was about-- about all the-- the nationalities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then when there were-- at towards the end of the war, they were bringing in death march.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Some of these trains came in with people who were in death march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were bringing them as-- as the Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they were bringing people completely decimated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember I had to pick up peels from these Hanover barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In-- in the basement, the potatoes were always stored in-- in-- in the cellars of these big barracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And people would be-- women would be peeling potatoes for the kitchens there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
